channel.title: My photoshop GFX
channel.description:
[size=20pt]Read the notes and wait for it to completely load![/size] First one, based off assasins creed desktop background, changed attributes, used smudge, used clone stamp tool, darken, color burn,lighten and used renders. Original:[IMG]http://assassinscreed.uk.ubi.com/wallpapers/wallpaper2_1024.jpg[/img] Mine:[IMG]http://i13.tinypic.com/6b4omro.png[/img]
2nd one, based off hitman blood money background, changed attributes, used smudge, clone stamp tool, lighting affects, darken, color burn and lighten. Original: [IMG]http://static.flickr.com/55/148600729_331029809d.jpg[/img] Mine:[IMG]http://i15.tinypic.com/52fn8ms.jpg[/img]
3rd one, based off a NFS Carbon screeny from IGN, changed attributes, used lighten, clonestamp tool, lighting effects, lighten and renders. Original:[IMG]http://www.nfscarbon.org/cars/need-for-speed-carbon-lamborgini-gallardo.jpg[/img] Mine:[IMG]http://i19.tinypic.com/6f4p10j.png[/img]
4th one, Based off nothing, I only took a screeny in Fable: TLC. I only Added Renders Together and lighten. Not much of a job but meh. Original:None Mine:[IMG]http://i15.tinypic.com/530jm15.jpg[/img]
5th one, Based off a Ronaldhinio Poster. Used Crop, Lighting, Renders (Small ones made by me) and Lens Flare. Original:[IMG]http://www.worldcupjapankorea.com/free-soccer-wallpapers/ronaldinho-wallpaper-barcelona.jpg[/img] Mine: [IMG]http://i9.tinypic.com/63tou0z.png[/img]
6th one, based off a FFS 7 Render, added effects to sword and renders to background.Also added black background to FFS 7 Render. Resized into sig. Original:[IMG]http://japanimation.com/jstore/figures/img/nr80690.gif[/img] Mine:[IMG]http://i12.tinypic.com/5zl92bl.png[/img]
Rate outta ten.

item.title: My photoshop GFX
item.dc:creator: @killerman93 killerman93
item.description:
@killerman93 wrote:

zammyking111:

I think the first one is ok the second one could do better and the third is really good but a little too bright

Nah its cos my mum hates nudity lol, so i needed enough light to block most of the female renders body out.

Uriko:

First ones the best IMHO. :/, woulda been better without that text.

Thanks for the tip, I put text so nobody would steal it and claim as their own on other forum.

soalreaver:

u totaly killed the assasins creed 1 sorry to say, the hitman… i guess thers to much of the same thing, and the NFS 1 is to light C&C lol

Lol, assassins creed was my first one :P, hitman was my 2nd and NFS needed to block out nudity (My mum doesnt like it).
